external_knowledge:
Alice Johnson is a user requesting information about inventory items;
The Austin area refers to the location with the name 'Austin';
Items of interest are those that have a connection to Alice Johnson through a request she has made.

sql:
SELECT inventory_items.item_name, requests.action
FROM inventory_items
JOIN requests ON inventory_items.item_id = requests.item_id;

SELECT request_id, user_id, status, response
FROM requests
WHERE action = 'Request Contact' AND status = 'Pending';
